node.text: August is the beginning of the turn towards darkness 🌚☀️🌹It’s almost time to say goodbye to nature’s bounty. By expressing your gratitude for your blessings in a ceremonial way, you invite more to follow. Prepare for the long farewell to summer with me as I read an excerpt from my Book of Blessings and Rituals, available on Amazon and all major bookstores.

node.title: The Book of Blessings & Rituals - A Reading with Athena Perrakis

node.text:
Are you ready to explore your spirituality and step into your full potential? 🦋🌙

Join Soul Shift Alchemize to expand your personal power, deepen your inner wisdom, and manifest joy, prosperity, and confidence. This online program will help you shift your mindset, so you feel more aligned and excited about your life and your future.

Alchemy is a process of transforming one substance, state of being, thought form, or creation into another. Alchemy is the process of becoming YOU – fully, passionately, and unapologetically.

It's never too late to start your healing journey, visit the link in bio to learn more and sign up for Soul Shift Alchemize.

node.text:
Happy Leo New Moon 🌑 🦁 ⠀
⠀
This is the most potent time to initiate new ideas, projects, and all kinds of new beginnings. The dark moon is full of possibility – you don’t need to know how things will unfold, you just need to take action to get it started. This is the time to set intentions based on your deepest desires, release fear, lean into faith, and trust your inner vision. To add to the magic, this New Moon is at the peak of Lion’s Gate, a serious vortex of star power that will empower your intentions.⠀
⠀
I have two online rituals for you today! My FREE online New Moon Ritual starts at 6 pm PT. I also prerecorded a Lion’s Gate Ritual you can watch today at 8 am or 8 pm in your own timezone. Find both links in the bio and stories! ⠀
⠀
✨ Gorgeous photo by @creativewannabe_

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sage Goddess on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'CRYSTALS FOR Tion's Gatệ GOLDEN CHALCEDONY Activates the Solar Plexus Chakra for confidence, courage, and willpower. ZIRCON Generates spontaneous manifestation, detoxifies, offers protection, and raises the vibration of all seven chakras. CARNELIAN Aids you in seeing projects through to completion and gives you the energy needed to bring your innermost dreams into reality GOLDEN SCAPOLITE Uplifts your mood, encourages confidence, supports successful outcomes, and helps you manifest your desires. @TheSageGoddess'.

node.text:
Lion's Gate reaches its peak tomorrow! 🦁⭐ The Sun and Leo are naturally associated with the Solar Plexus Chakra, the energy center that sits about three inches above the navel and is the seat of your personal power. The Lion’s Gate portal is an invitation to accept and amplify your own power and use it in ever-expanding ways. A balanced Solar Plexus Chakra manifests as self-confidence, healthy self-control, and willpower. It directly correlates to prosperity and the entire cycle of manifestation. If you’ve been struggling with finances, you can use this energy portal to guide your stream of thought in the direction of abundance and tap into the frequency and flow of money and resources.⠀
⠀
Here are some stone recommendations for tomorrow's big event! Don't miss my free online ritual! Link in bio to learn more 💫

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sage Goddess on August 06, 2021.

node.text:
Activating the Crown Chakra today with my favorite purple stones 💜 👑 ⠀
⠀
The Crown Chakra resonates with wisdom, connection to the spiritual realms, and attunement with the Universe. Activate this energy center to go beyond the personal and immerse yourself completely in the ineffable reality of love, bliss, and pure awareness that is Source.⠀
⠀
To activate your Crown Chakra, compose a prayer or invocation, or choose a mantra that feels resonant with your energy right now. Ask for help, and call on your spirit guides, angels, or ascended masters. If you'd like to learn more about the chakras, follow the link in bio to read my blog. ⠀
⠀
What types of activities do you do for chakra healing?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sage Goddess on August 05, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: The Lion’s Gate Portal is OPEN ✨🦁🤩 This is one of THE most powerful times for manifestation. You’re always creating your reality, but when the Gate is open, everything moves faster and with intensified energy. This energy peaks on 8/8 at 8 am or pm in your own time zone. I recorded a free online meditation for you to watch. Link in bio to learn more!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sage Goddess on August 04, 2021. May be an image of candle.

node.text: It's Prayer Wednesday and our candles are lit🕯️💜 If you have anything weighing on your mind and heart, leave it in the comments so we can hold it together. You don't have to go through anything alone. Sending lots of love from all of SG.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sage Goddess on August 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'This year we have New Moon during the peak of the Lion's Gate portal! This rare event is a powerful opportunity for manifestation. When the portal is open, everything moves faster and with intensified energy. SAGEGODDESS.COM'.

node.text:
Get ready, there’s a rare New Moon on Lion’s Gate 🤩🦁r⠀
⠀
Sunday's New Moon in Leo is bringing us all together, and, at the peak of Lion’s Gate, it’s a powerful time for Soul Star Chakra activation - our connection to star beings, planets, and other dimensions. Leo Moon is star power! Seriously, Leo is ruled by the star we call our Sun, and your intentions will receive an extra boost on the peak of Lion’s Gate. We’re all made of stardust. You are a star among stars. I’m holding a free online ritual to celebrate and guide you in setting intentions. Link in bio to learn more. ⠀
⠀
Make sure to tag your moon sisters! This is going to be big 🌟 💫

node.text: August is the beginning of the turn towards darkness 🌚☀️🌹It’s almost time to say goodbye to nature’s bounty. By expressing your gratitude for your blessings in a ceremonial way, you invite more to follow. Prepare for the long farewell to summer with me as I read an excerpt from my Book of Blessings and Rituals, available on Amazon and all major bookstores.

node.text:
Happy Lammas and First Harvest 🌾 🧡 ☀️⠀
⠀
At this time of year, the nights are beginning to lengthen, and we anticipate the return of fall. Before the Wheel turns to the darker months, we can take time to appreciate warmth and sunlight and how they support the season of growth. During Lammas, take a moment to reflect on the first half of this year and what has carried over from the last year. Now is the time to make peace with the year behind us and focus on what we can harvest from that trying, transformative experience. ⠀
⠀
This year, we’re working with the Fibonacci spiral and the sunflower to honor Lammas. In tonight's ritual, we'll powerfully harness the energy of Lammas and call prosperity into all facets of our lives. My live online event is free to join! Link in bio to join me live on YouTube at 6 pm PT 🌟

Here comes August ☀️ 🌟 🏖️⠀
⠀
This is the month to accelerate your personal growth! Leo season plus the peak of Lion's gate is giving us serious star power. We’re all made of stardust and you are a star among stars. Take the leap no matter how scary it may seem. The universe has your back. What are you ready to accomplish? Name it and claim it in the comments!

node.text: Perfume Around the World starts today 🙌💜🌍🌸Are you excited? Perfume Around the World is a three-month perfumery and aromatherapy experience that will transport your senses to a different civilization each month. Together, we’ll blend signature oils from each region to create our own custom blends, learn the history of aromatherapy in each region, and the use of herbs and fragrances in spiritual and ceremonial practice. Classes are recorded and you can watch as many times as you’d like! Learn more and register on SageGoddess.com. Link in bio!
